## Installation

```bash
git clone https://github.com/rtl-gen-aii/rtl-gen-aii
cd rtl-gen-aii
pip install -e .
```

## Quick Start
```bash
python -m python.__main__ "Generate an 8-bit D-Flipflop"
```

